{"id":4491,"date":"2024-09-05T01:13:15","date_gmt":"2024-09-04T16:13:15","guid":{"rendered":"https://blogbooks.net/?p=4491"},"modified":"2024-09-05T01:13:19","modified_gmt":"2024-09-04T16:13:19","slug":"chromeos%e3%82%a8%e3%83%9f%e3%83%a5%e3%83%ac%e3%83%bc%e3%82%bf%e3%83%bc-anuraos","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/4491/","title":{"rendered":"ChromeOSエミュレーター AnuraOS"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>こんにちはPsanです。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>今回は、Web上で動作するChromeOSのエミュレーターを紹介します。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>このプロジェクトは、MercuryWorkshopという開発グループのものです。</p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>ソースコード<br><a href=\"https://github.com/MercuryWorkshop/anuraOS\">https://github.com/MercuryWorkshop/anuraOS</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">AnuraOSとは？</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Webサイト上でエミュレートできる、Chromium OSに似た仮想Linux環境です<br>Google Chrome, Firefox, Safariで動作します。</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">実際に動かす</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>まず、<a href=\"https://anura.pro/\">https://anura.pro/</a>　にアクセスします。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" data-attachment-id=\"4499\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/4491/attachment/screenshot-2024-08-23-07-19-32/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.19.32.png\" data-orig-size=\"1920,1200\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot 2024-08-23 07.19.32\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.19.32-300x188.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.19.32-1024x640.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.19.32-1024x640.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4499\" style=\"width:437px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.19.32-1024x640.png 1024w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.19.32-300x188.png 300w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.19.32-768x480.png 768w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.19.32-1536x960.png 1536w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.19.32.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>次にNextを押します。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>LinuxなどのRootfsを入れて、Linuxのコマンドが使いたい人は、</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alphin Debian Arch　の3つが用意されています。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Linuxを使わない人は、Normal User を選択してください。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>また、ダウンロードして実行しない場合は、No Download　を選択してください。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" data-attachment-id=\"4500\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/4491/attachment/screenshot-2024-08-23-07-20-28/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.20.28.png\" data-orig-size=\"1920,1200\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot 2024-08-23 07.20.28\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.20.28-300x188.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.20.28-1024x640.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.20.28-1024x640.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4500\" style=\"width:614px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.20.28-1024x640.png 1024w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.20.28-300x188.png 300w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.20.28-768x480.png 768w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.20.28-1536x960.png 1536w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot-2024-08-23-07.20.28.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>すると、セットアップが開始されるので、しばらく待つと、AnuraOSが起動します。</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">自分でAnuraOSをホストする Ubuntu</h2>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>sudo apt install -y nodejs npm wget default-jdk inotify-tools rustc cargo make gcc docker.io\nrustup target add wasm32-unknown-unknown</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>リポジトリのクローン</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>git clone --recursive https://github.com/MercuryWorkshop/anuraOS</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>makeの実行</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>cd anuraOS\nmake all</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>Rootfsを作る場合</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>make rootfs</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>選択肢が出てきたら、4を押します。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>起動する</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>make server</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>http://localhost:8000　にアクセスします。</p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"こんにちはPsanです。\n今回は、Web上で動作するChromeOSのエミュレーターを紹